---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const packages = [
  { title: 'Standard Package', description: '25-30 professional photos covering all spaces. Perfect for most 1-2 bedroom properties.' },
  { title: 'Premium Package', description: '40+ photos including twilight/golden hour shots. Ideal for luxury listings.' },
  { title: 'Video Tour', description: '60-90 second walkthrough video. Great for larger properties and unique spaces.' },
  { title: 'Twilight Shots', description: 'Dramatic evening photos showcasing city views and ambiance.' },
  { title: 'Drone Photography', description: 'Aerial shots for properties with impressive locations or views.' },
  { title: 'Seasonal Updates', description: 'Fresh photos each season to keep your listing current.' }
];

const relatedServices = [
  { name: 'Full Management', href: '/services/full-airbnb-management-toronto' },
  { name: 'Listing Optimization', href: '/services/airbnb-listing-optimization-toronto' },
  { name: 'Dynamic Pricing', href: '/services/airbnb-dynamic-pricing-toronto' },
  { name: 'Cleaning Services', href: '/services/airbnb-cleaning-toronto' }
];

const serviceAreas = [
  { name: 'Downtown Toronto', href: '/downtown-toronto-airbnb-management' },
  { name: 'North York', href: '/north-york-airbnb-management' },
  { name: 'Mississauga', href: '/mississauga-airbnb-management' },
  { name: 'Scarborough', href: '/scarborough-airbnb-management' },
  { name: 'Etobicoke', href: '/etobicoke-airbnb-management' }
];

const includes = [
  '25-40 edited photos',
  'HDR processing',
  'Professional equipment',
  'Staging guidance',
  '48-hour delivery',
  'Airbnb-optimized sizing'
];
---

<Layout title="Airbnb Photography Toronto & GTA | Professional Listing Photos" description="Professional Airbnb photography in Toronto and the Greater Toronto Area. Stunning listing photos that get more bookings at higher rates. HDR, twilight shots, and drone photography available.">
  <section class="hero hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Professional <span class="highlight">Airbnb Photography</span> Toronto</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Stunning photos that stop scrollers and convert browsers into bookers. The single highest-ROI investment for your listing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="trust-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trust-grid">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">24%</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Higher Rates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">40%</span>
          <span class="trust-label">More Bookings</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">2x</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Faster Booking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">48hr</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Photo Delivery</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <p class="intro-text">Airbnb is a visual platform. Guests scroll through dozens of listings, and you have about 2 seconds to grab their attention. Professional photos are the difference between getting clicked and getting skipped.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> 25-40 HDR-processed photos</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Professional equipment and lighting</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Staging guidance included</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Twilight and drone options</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Airbnb-optimized sizing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book Photo Shoot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="main-content">
          <h2>Why Professional Photos Matter</h2>
          <p>Airbnb is a visual platform. Guests scroll through dozens of listings, and you have about 2 seconds to grab their attention. Professional photos are the difference between getting clicked and getting skipped.</p>

          <p>According to Airbnb's own data, listings with professional photos earn up to 40% more than those with amateur shots. That's not a small improvement — it's the difference between breaking even and profitable hosting.</p>

          <div class="comparison-grid">
            <div class="comparison-card">
              <h4>DIY Phone Photos</h4>
              <p>Average nightly rate</p>
              <span class="result">$125</span>
            </div>
            <div class="comparison-card highlight">
              <h4>Professional Photos</h4>
              <p>Average nightly rate</p>
              <span class="result">$155</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p>That's $30/night more — or $900+/month at typical occupancy. Professional photos pay for themselves within days.</p>

          <h3>What We Photograph</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Hero Shot:</strong> The first photo that appears in search results. Usually living room or stunning view.</li>
            <li><strong>All Rooms:</strong> Bedrooms, bathrooms, kitchen, living areas — each from multiple angles.</li>
            <li><strong>Details:</strong> Amenities, decor touches, welcome items that show your property's personality.</li>
            <li><strong>Outdoor Spaces:</strong> Balconies, patios, building amenities, pool, parking.</li>
            <li><strong>Building & Location:</strong> Exterior shots, neighborhood highlights, nearby attractions.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Photography Tips for Higher Bookings</h3>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <h4>Tip #1: Declutter Ruthlessly</h4>
            <p>Less is more. Remove personal items, excessive decorations, and anything that makes spaces look small. Clean surfaces photograph better than busy ones.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <h4>Tip #2: Lighting is Everything</h4>
            <p>We shoot during optimal natural light (usually mid-morning). All lights on, curtains open, no harsh shadows. This is why professional timing matters.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <h4>Tip #3: Stage Like a Hotel</h4>
            <p>Fluffy white towels fanned on beds, fresh flowers on tables, coffee cups arranged aesthetically. These "lifestyle" shots help guests imagine themselves there.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <h4>Tip #4: Highlight What's Unique</h4>
            <p>CN Tower view? Photograph it. Amazing kitchen? Multiple angles. Hot tub? Make it the hero. Your unique features should dominate the photo set.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <h4>Tip #5: Order Matters</h4>
            <p>Your first 5 photos appear in Airbnb's preview. Lead with your best shot, then bedroom, then kitchen/living. Bathroom photos should come later.</p>
          </div>

          <h3>Our Photography Process</h3>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Consultation:</strong> We discuss your property's best features and target guest.</li>
            <li><strong>Prep Guidance:</strong> We send a checklist to prepare your space for the shoot.</li>
            <li><strong>Photo Shoot:</strong> 1-2 hours on-site with professional equipment.</li>
            <li><strong>Editing:</strong> HDR processing, color correction, and enhancement.</li>
            <li><strong>Delivery:</strong> High-resolution images optimized for Airbnb within 48 hours.</li>
            <li><strong>Upload Support:</strong> We can upload and arrange photos on your listing.</li>
          </ol>

          <h3>Included with Full Management</h3>
          <p>Professional photography is included at no extra cost with our <a href="/services/full-airbnb-management-toronto">full management service</a>. We also include seasonal photo updates and re-shoots if you make significant changes to your property.</p>
        </div>

        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-cta">
            <h4>Book a Shoot</h4>
            <p>Transform your listing with professional photos.</p>
            <a href="tel:647-957-8956" class="btn btn-primary">Call 647-957-8956</a>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Related Services</h4>
            <ul>
              {relatedServices.map(service => (
                <li><a href={service.href}>{service.name}</a></li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Service Areas</h4>
            <ul>
              {serviceAreas.map(area => (
                <li><a href={area.href}>{area.name}</a></li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>What's Included</h4>
            <ul>
              {includes.map(item => (
                <li>{item}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section packages-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Photography Packages</h2>
        <p>Options for every property type</p>
      </div>
      <div class="packages-grid">
        {packages.map(pkg => (
          <div class="package-card">
            <h3>{pkg.title}</h3>
            <p>{pkg.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section related-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Complete Your Listing Optimization</h2>
        <p>Photography works best with these services</p>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid">
        <a href="/services/airbnb-listing-optimization-toronto" class="related-card">
          <h4>Listing Optimization</h4>
          <p>SEO-optimized titles and descriptions</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/airbnb-dynamic-pricing-toronto" class="related-card">
          <h4>Dynamic Pricing</h4>
          <p>Maximize your newly improved listing</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/full-airbnb-management-toronto" class="related-card">
          <h4>Full Management</h4>
          <p>Photography included at no extra cost</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/airbnb-cleaning-toronto" class="related-card">
          <h4>Cleaning Services</h4>
          <p>Keep your space photo-ready</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/airbnb-turnover-management-toronto" class="related-card">
          <h4>Turnover Management</h4>
          <p>Maintain that perfect look</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/toronto-airbnb-not-making-money" class="related-card">
          <h4>Improve Revenue</h4>
          <p>Complete revenue optimization guide</p>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Listing?</h2>
        <p>Professional photos pay for themselves within days. Book your shoot today.</p>
        <a href="tel:647-957-8956" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Call Now: 647-957-8956</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background-alt) 0%, var(--color-background) 100%);
  }

  .hero-small h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-bar {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .trust-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-item {
    color: white;
  }

  .trust-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .trust-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .intro-section {
    background: white;
  }

  .intro-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .check {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content-section {
    background: white;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .main-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .main-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .main-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .main-content ul, .main-content ol {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .main-content li {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .main-content a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .comparison-card {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .comparison-card.highlight {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    color: white;
  }

